{"comments":"Frosted — blur + tint + noise compound for glassmorphism effects.\n\n## Purpose\n\nThe Frosted compound represents the three essential components of\nfrosted glass / glassmorphism effects as pure data:\n\n1. **Blur**: Background blur radius\n2. **Tint**: Color overlay with opacity\n3. **Noise**: Texture to prevent color banding\n\nThis is **pure data**. The runtime (WebGPU, Canvas, etc.) interprets\nthese values into actual rendering commands. No CSS, no JavaScript,\nno browser assumptions.\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Schema.Material.BlurRadius (blur amount)\n- Schema.Color.SRGB (tint color)\n- Schema.Color.Opacity (transparency)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["blurRadius",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["tintColor",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","SRGB"],"SRGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["tintOpacity",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["noiseOpacity",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["noiseScale",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Frosted.purs","start":[95,17]},"title":"Frosted"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema